author: Sara Randazzo
title: Judge Asks Dewey Jurors to Return With Another Partial Verdict
text:
A judge asked jurors deliberating in the financial fraud trial of three former Dewey & LeBoeuf LLP leaders to return with a partial verdict Tuesday after they said they continue to be deadlocked on the majority of charges.
